The api can be initialised by running the index.js file using the command node index.js. The program will listen to port 4000 on the local host.
you can get the list of stores typing localhost:4000/api/stores into the browser. A store can be added by posting raw json text to localhost:4000/api/stores.
An store can be deleted by sending a delete request to localhost:4000/api/stores/:storeid. the id can be obtained by from issuing a get command to localhost:4000/api/stores.
a stores info can be altered by sending raw json text to localhost:4000/api/stores/:storeid. The list of dependancies is located in the package.json file and can be installed
using the command npm install in the terminal.
